                                    {
                                        "Document": "IG v3.4",
                                        "Section": "4.4.7",
                                        "Cited_Guidance": "If the reference time point is prior to the date of collection or assessment: Start values: an observation can start BEFORE the reference point, can start COINCIDENT with the reference point, can start AFTER the reference point, or it may not be known (U) when it started. End values: an observation can end BEFORE the reference point, can end COINCIDENT with the reference point, can end AFTER the reference point, can be known that it didn't end but was ONGOING, or it is unknown (U) when it ended or if it was ongoing."
                                    }
                                ],
